-- ‚ēź‚ēź LOADING SCREEN ‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź
function Nexus:LoadingScreen(opts)
    opts  = opts or {}
    local title = opts.Title    or "NexusUI"
    local sub   = opts.Subtitle or "Initializing..."
    local tasks = opts.Tasks    or {}
    local T = (type(opts.Theme) == "table") and opts.Theme
              or Nexus.Themes[opts.Theme] or Nexus.Themes.Void

    local sg  = mkGui(99999)
    local bg  = N("Frame", {Size=UDim2.new(1,0,1,0), BackgroundColor3=T.bg, BorderSizePixel=0, ZIndex=1, Parent=sg})
    -- Ambient dot grid
    N("ImageLabel", {Size=UDim2.new(0,700,0,700), Position=UDim2.new(.5,-350,.5,-350),
        BackgroundTransparency=1, Image="rbxassetid://6014261993",
        ImageColor3=T.accent, ImageTransparency=.94, ZIndex=2, Parent=bg})

    local vp   = getVP()
    local CW   = math.min(420, vp.X-60)
    local CH   = 250 + #tasks*28
    local card = N("Frame", {Size=UDim2.new(0,CW,0,CH), AnchorPoint=Vector2.new(.5,.5),
        Position=UDim2.new(.5,0,.54,0), BackgroundColor3=T.section,
        BackgroundTransparency=1, BorderSizePixel=0, ZIndex=3, Parent=bg})
    N("UICorner", {CornerRadius=UDim.new(0,CR_WIN), Parent=card})
    N("UIStroke",  {Color=T.border, Thickness=1, Transparency=.15, Parent=card})

    -- Animated top accent stripe
    local stripe = N("Frame", {Size=UDim2.new(0,0,0,2), BackgroundColor3=T.accent,
        BorderSizePixel=0, ZIndex=4, Parent=card})
    N("UICorner", {CornerRadius=UDim.new(0,2), Parent=stripe})
    local shimmer = N("Frame", {Size=UDim2.new(0,90,1,0), Position=UDim2.new(-.15,0,0,0),
        BackgroundColor3=T.accentH, BackgroundTransparency=.5,
        BorderSizePixel=0, ZIndex=5, Parent=stripe})
    N("UIGradient", {Transparency=NumberSequence.new({
        NumberSequenceKeypoint.new(0,1), NumberSequenceKeypoint.new(0.35,0.2),
        NumberSequenceKeypoint.new(0.65,0.2), NumberSequenceKeypoint.new(1,1)
    }), Parent=shimmer})
    tw(card, .5, {BackgroundTransparency=0, Position=UDim2.new(.5,0,.5,0)})

    local y = 30
    -- Accent dot
    local adot = N("Frame", {Size=UDim2.new(0,8,0,8), AnchorPoint=Vector2.new(.5,.5),
        Position=UDim2.new(0,20,0,y+10), BackgroundColor3=T.accent,
        BorderSizePixel=0, ZIndex=5, Parent=card})
    N("UICorner", {CornerRadius=UDim.new(1,0), Parent=adot})
    N("TextLabel", {Size=UDim2.new(1,-38,0,30), Position=UDim2.new(0,28,0,y-2),
        BackgroundTransparency=1, Text=title, TextColor3=T.text, TextSize=22,
        Font=Enum.Font.GothamBold, ZIndex=4, Parent=card}); y=y+36
    local subLbl = N("TextLabel", {Size=UDim2.new(1,-32,0,16), Position=UDim2.new(0,16,0,y),
        BackgroundTransparency=1, Text=sub, TextColor3=T.sub, TextSize=12,
        Font=Enum.Font.Gotham, ZIndex=4, Parent=card}); y=y+28

    local checks = {}
    for i, tk in ipairs(tasks) do
        local row = N("Frame", {Size=UDim2.new(1,-32,0,24), Position=UDim2.new(0,16,0,y),
            BackgroundTransparency=1, ZIndex=4, Parent=card})
        local dot = N("Frame", {Size=UDim2.new(0,7,0,7), AnchorPoint=Vector2.new(0,.5),
            Position=UDim2.new(0,0,.5,0), BackgroundColor3=T.muted,
            BorderSizePixel=0, ZIndex=5, Parent=row})
        N("UICorner", {CornerRadius=UDim.new(1,0), Parent=dot})
        local tl = N("TextLabel", {Size=UDim2.new(1,-18,1,0), Position=UDim2.new(0,16,0,0),
            BackgroundTransparency=1, Text=tk.Name or ("Task "..i), TextColor3=T.muted,
            TextSize=12, Font=Enum.Font.Gotham, TextXAlignment=Enum.TextXAlignment.Left, ZIndex=5, Parent=row})
        checks[i] = {dot=dot, lbl=tl}; y=y+26
    end
    y=y+10

    local track = N("Frame", {Size=UDim2.new(1,-32,0,5), Position=UDim2.new(0,16,0,y),
        BackgroundColor3=T.border, BorderSizePixel=0, ZIndex=4, Parent=card})
    N("UICorner", {CornerRadius=UDim.new(1,0), Parent=track})
    local barFill = N("Frame", {Size=UDim2.new(0,0,1,0), BackgroundColor3=T.accent,
        BorderSizePixel=0, ZIndex=5, Parent=track})
    N("UICorner", {CornerRadius=UDim.new(1,0), Parent=barFill}); y=y+14

    local pctL = N("TextLabel", {Size=UDim2.new(.5,0,0,16), Position=UDim2.new(.5,0,0,y),
        BackgroundTransparency=1, Text="0%", TextColor3=T.accent, TextSize=11,
        Font=Enum.Font.GothamBold, TextXAlignment=Enum.TextXAlignment.Right, ZIndex=4, Parent=card})

    -- Animated shimmer loop
    local function animShimmer()
        shimmer.Position = UDim2.new(-.2,0,0,0)
        TweenService:Create(shimmer, TweenInfo.new(1.4, Enum.EasingStyle.Sine, Enum.EasingDirection.InOut, -1, false), {Position=UDim2.new(1.1,0,0,0)}):Play()
    end
    task.delay(.5, animShimmer)

    local done  = 0
    local total = math.max(1, #tasks)
    local Screen = {}

    function Screen:Task(i, success)
        done = done + (success ~= false and 1 or 0)
        if checks[i] then
            local c = success ~= false and T.success or T.error
            tw(checks[i].dot, .2, {BackgroundColor3=c})
            tw(checks[i].lbl, .2, {TextColor3=c})
        end
        local pct = done/total
        tw(barFill, .3, {Size=UDim2.new(pct,0,1,0)})
        pctL.Text = math.floor(pct*100).."%"
    end
    function Screen:SetSubtitle(t) subLbl.Text = t end
    function Screen:Dismiss(delay2)
        task.delay(delay2 or 0, function()
            twI(card, .28, {BackgroundTransparency=1, Size=UDim2.new(0,CW*.6,0,CH*.6)})
            twI(bg,   .4,  {BackgroundTransparency=1})
            task.delay(.42, function() pcall(function() sg:Destroy() end) end)
        end)
    end
    return Screen
end

